

ENGINE Command

SYNOPSIS
    b_addborder <name> <internode> 


DESCRIPTION
    This command adds a border transport to a Accelero node.
    The b_settype, b_setfamily, and b_setmods commands must
    be executed before this command.  Optionally, the b_setspecs,
    b_setcallbacks, and b_addlink commands may also be performed
    before this command.

PARAMETERS
    <name>                Test Name
    <internode>           yes|no


EXAMPLE

    b_addborder New-Transport-27 no
